DescDetail: <<
This package defines basic operations on intervals. It is useful when some
values for a computation are uncertain.

It provides the following functions:
	addInt
	negateInt
	subInt
	mulInt
	invertInt
	invertAddInt
	divInt
	powerInt
	sqrInt
	sqrtInt
	addSqrInt
	engFormInt
	intFormInt
	dB10ToLinInt
	linToDB10Int
	dB20ToLinInt
	linToDB20Int
	valtol100ToInt
	intToTol
	intToTol100
	intToVal
	linSpaceTol100Int
	logSpaceTol100Int
	monotonicFunctionInt
	functionInt
	plotInt
	errorBarInt
<<

